{"tid":1395372,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"香港市民應開始拒絕承認警察的執法權力","createTime":"2019-08-01T17:22:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-01T17:30:36.000Z","uid":167878,"like":39,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"ca4f8b46e06931257e2423272bad9614d89f22f9","tid":1395372,"uid":167878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T17:22:46.000Z","msg":"警察再無資格進行執法角色<br />\n香港市民要拒絕承認警察執法嘅權力<br />\n由香港人代替佢地執行所謂嘅警權<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.taitau.net/power/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.taitau.net%2Fpower%2F&d=oOhF4K9gmG%2F73F8T9h6VFBVENBC9VnKGSHAjWoGsWeM%3D&h=68bcf240\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.taitau.net/power/</a><br />\n<br />\n香港人應該令警察執唔到任何法<br />\n我地無須再遵從警察任何指令<br />\ncheck身份證 搜身 協助警察調查之類<br />\n<br />\n甚至應該阻止警察執法<br />\n就算係捉人橫過馬路 隨地扔垃圾<br />\n嗰d人由我地香港市民自己嚟捉<br />\n我咁講亦唔係鼓勵香港人犯法 <br />\n而係叫香港人自己取代警察執法<br />\n<br />\n因為而家嘅警察永遠企住人民對立面<br />\n多次對香港市民不公平地執法<br />\n又與三合會合作對香港市民進行恐怖襲擊<br />\n其後又用催淚彈 橡膠子彈保護返班黑社會<br />\n<br />\n以後如果比撐警人士打 <br />\n香港市民應自行做相對應行動<br />\n無須想聯絡警察 因為佢地會放走班犯罪分子"},{"pid":"4c56663b212bc32ab4d01af447ea755e44f4cef1","tid":1395372,"uid":167878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T17:23:19.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">麻包袋</span></span>"},{"pid":"341768b68c3bdd23b6ecff79f7b47dd4aec1a4d4","tid":1395372,"uid":167878,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T17:23:35.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">麻包袋</span></span>"},{"pid":"776e10f6ec862142a75b443b57dfd6e6e937b3f1","tid":1395372,"uid":167878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T17:23:45.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">麻包袋</span></span>"},{"pid":"e1ede9fceb2f05d7e27d4e3cc59b1996f7fbba40","tid":1395372,"uid":167878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T17:23:55.000Z","msg":"<span sty